#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.69"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.69:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.69:0.2"
msgid "7. Pattakammavagga"
msgstr "7. Deeds of Substance"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.69:0.3"
msgid "69. Padhānasutta"
msgstr "69. Effort"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.74"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.69:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, padhānāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four efforts."

msgctxt "an4.69:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.69:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saṃvarappadhānaṃ, pahānappadhānaṃ, bhāvanāppadhānaṃ, anurakkhaṇāppadhānaṃ."
msgstr "The efforts to restrain, to give up, to develop, and to preserve."

msgctxt "an4.69:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, saṃvarappadhānaṃ?"
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to restrain?"

msgctxt "an4.69:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti "
"padahati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and "
"strive so that bad, unskillful qualities don’t arise."

msgctxt "an4.69:1.6"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saṃvarappadhānaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the effort to restrain."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.69:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, pahānappadhānaṃ?"
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to give up?"

msgctxt "an4.69:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya "
"chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and "
"strive so that bad, unskillful qualities are given up."

msgctxt "an4.69:2.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pahānappadhānaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the effort to give up."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.69:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, bhāvanāppadhānaṃ?"
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to develop?"

msgctxt "an4.69:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya chandaṃ "
"janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and "
"strive so that skillful qualities arise."

msgctxt "an4.69:3.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhāvanāppadhānaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the effort to develop."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.69:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, anurakkhaṇāppadhānaṃ?"
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the effort to preserve?"

msgctxt "an4.69:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya "
"bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ "
"ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when you generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and "
"strive so that skillful qualities that have arisen remain, are not lost, but "
"increase, mature, and are fulfilled by development."

msgctxt "an4.69:4.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, anurakkhaṇāppadhānaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the effort to preserve."

msgctxt "an4.69:4.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri padhānānīti."
msgstr "These are the four efforts."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.1"
msgid "Saṃvaro ca pahānañca,"
msgstr "Restraint and giving up,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.2"
msgid "bhāvanā anurakkhaṇā;"
msgstr "development and preservation:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.3"
msgid "Ete padhānā cattāro,"
msgstr "these are the four efforts"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.4"
msgid "desitādiccabandhunā;"
msgstr "taught by the Kinsman of the Sun."

#. <br>
#. VAR: hi → yehi (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.69:5.5"
msgid "Yo hi bhikkhu idhātāpī,"
msgstr "Any mendicant who keenly applies these"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.69:5.6"
msgid "khayaṃ dukkhassa pāpuṇe”ti."
msgstr "may attain the ending of suffering.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.69:5.7"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
